 />\n<br />\n现在有TB店想出青鸟同款长笛双簧管的模型（还有丽久的同款），感觉这个可以有，之前看原po的图就是觉得不够还原所以犹豫了没买。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1538","username":"Acatv","adminid":"0","groupid":"30","memberstatus":"0","number":"1537","dbdateline":"1544696948","groupiconid":"6"},{"pid":"41933418","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"osore","authorid":"184969","dateline":"2018-12-13 18:48","message":"感觉希美除了みぞれ以外不怎么主动找人玩<br />\r\n高三寒假（12.24）中午在街上遇到夏纪，也是夏纪主动邀她吃饭<br />\r\n然后她说寒假没人陪她玩，夏纪说你可以找我wwwwww<br />\r\nTV第二季泳装回也是夏纪邀她","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1539","username":"osore","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1538","dbdateline":"1544698114","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41933793","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"zhjnppy","authorid":"421795","dateline":"2018-12-13 19:26","message":"刚查了下10号下单的限定版还没开始配送 信用卡已经扣款了不会砍单吧<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/001.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coolapk.com/apk/140634\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 有消息提醒的 Stage1官方 Android客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1540","username":"zhjnppy","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"1539","dbdateline":"1544700368","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41933958","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"supersssbc","authorid":"197006","dateline":"2018-12-13 19:40","message":"日亚上除了通常版剩下3种连补货预感都没了。。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"1541","username":"supersssbc","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"1540","dbdateline":"1544701242","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41934266","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Bani82","authorid":"105209","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:13","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41933418&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">osore 发表于 2018-12-13 18:48</font></a><br />\r\n感觉希美除了みぞれ以外不怎么主动找人玩<br />\r\n高三寒假（12.24）中午在街上遇到夏纪，也是夏纪主动邀她吃饭<br />\r\n然 ...</div><br />\n那么她有没有去找Mizore玩呢！","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1542","username":"Bani82","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1541","dbdateline":"1544703210","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41934302","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"zhangyichi26","authorid":"393862","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:17","message":"<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201812/13/200017yinummi4m41lg4mi.jpg\" attach=\"41934302\" /></div><br />\r\n电子表之前有人考据出来了。感觉定位其实类似普通人家给孩子的礼物这样子吧？（照这么看伞哥家里人之间关系应该挺好的<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/074.png\" />）<br />\r\n说“穷”确实有点夸张，不过肯定算不上特别富裕，事实上伞哥放弃音大确实一定程度上跟家庭条件有关……<br />\r\n乐器、私教各种前期投入（还有比起普通大学更加昂贵的学费）如果只是为了进音大做一个“普通学生”的话，伞哥的家庭条件显然蛮难支撑起这种“玩票”的。<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1543","username":"zhangyichi26","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"1542","dbdateline":"1544703442","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41934371","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"MikiyaKokutou","authorid":"448629","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:25","message":"抽时间又重温了一遍第二季前5话<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希美是真心喜欢みぞれ的双簧管啊，两人在教室和好时希美说的也是我喜欢你演奏的双簧管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且希美也是真心嫉妒みぞれ啊，虽然TV二期没明示嫉妒她在音乐上的才能，但是武本泳装回时，希美对久美子说自己不甘心退部后第二年就进了关西大赛，みぞれ又是正赛成员（画重点！），镜头马上给到了希美手中饮料罐外凝结的水珠，这点小心思……<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新山老师是真的欣赏みぞれ，后者被批后马上进行一对一心灵辅导，还说可能是我对你要求太高了，果然慧眼识珠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都说第4话高潮矫情，我倒觉得前三话拍的都相当一般，包括武本回，但第4话四人间的那点小思绪拍的真好，虽然两年前我就夸过这里了。<br />\r\n优子也好夏纪也好，两年后的我愈加感同身受了。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1544","username":"MikiyaKokutou","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"1543","dbdateline":"1544703900","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41934417","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:29","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41924950&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Maestro 发表于 2018-12-13 00:14</font></a><br />\r\n知乎上最高赞的回答里有对倒三角的解读<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/274282069/answer/546484292\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/274282069/answer/546484292</a></div>38.26，<br />\r<div class=\"reply_wrap\">窗户上的红色三角标记是11区的消防标记，带有红色三角标记的窗户便于从外部击破。一旦发生火灾，消防队可以根据该标记破窗进入，从而提高救援效率</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知乎这个回答虽然提到了三角，但是也没说三角是什么意思？还是我没看懂？<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1545","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"1544","dbdateline":"1544704173","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41934438","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"MikiyaKokutou","authorid":"448629","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:31","message":"讲道理，高中生戴600块钱的电子表，非常典型的工薪家庭吧。家境尚可的基本都是万元以上的机械表吧，起码我十年前上高中的时候就这样了。<br />\n<br />\n后来原著也提到过希美上大学后没租房住，因为顾虑房租太贵。<br />\n<br />\n正好重温了下TV二期，里面有希美房间的画面，怎么讲，房间比较小，装饰的还不错，估计家境应该比三香强些，但也强的有限。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1546","username":"MikiyaKokutou","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"1545","dbdateline":"1544704265","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41934528","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"osore","authorid":"184969","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:39","message":"<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/065.png\" />小黄也戴个表，不知道哪个更贵","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1547","username":"osore","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1546","dbdateline":"1544704795","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41934613","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"傘木希美","authorid":"506425","dateline":"2018-12-13 20:47","message":"说来，为啥有的楼层，好多留白啊，往下滑时要滑好久…<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coolapk.com/apk/140